➜初秋漫步凉水河畔金色花海
http://www.sohu.com/a/420271079_115865	12342
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200923/7efa4911872145e8b4a690cf5e43627b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
